      <description>&lt;p&gt;I’ve been working on a Shiny web app to visualize the results from a text classification algorithm. Specifically, the app aims to classify a particular document in Spanish as either approximating the usage from one of three Spanish subvarieties: Argentine, Mexican, and Peninsular.&lt;/p&gt;
